OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer hailed the long-
OL,8,Fdelayed plan for defence spending as a
OL,9,Fgame-changing move that will keep the
OL,10,FUK "safe and secure long into the
OL,11,Ffuture" as he announced it will be
OL,12,Fpublished on Tuesday.
OL,14,FThe defence investment plan (Dip),
OL,15,Foriginally due last year, had been
OL,16,Fheld back amid wrangling within
OL,17,FGovernment over the amount of money
OL,18,Frequired to finance the military.
OL,26,@rD@DOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
