OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FFormer defence secretary John Healey
OL,8,Fquit in protest over it, as he did not
OL,9,Fbelieve the Dip provided enough
OL,10,Ffunding for the UK to transform its
OL,11,Farmed forces and meet future threats.
OL,13,FHe also warned that the plan would
OL,14,Flikely fall short of Britain's
OL,15,Fcommitments to the Nato alliance,
OL,16,Fwhich has tasked all member states
OL,17,Fwith hiking core defence spending to
OL,18,F3.5% of national economic output by
OL,19,F2035.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FUnder the stewardship of new Defence
OL,8,FSecretary Dan Jarvis, the Dip will now
OL,9,Ffocus on ramping up the UK's use of
OL,10,Fdrones and autonomous weapons, funded
OL,11,Fby a #5 billion investment, the
OL,12,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) has
OL,13,Fannounced.
OL,15,FHe is understood to have secured some
OL,16,Fextra money for the plan, taking the
OL,17,Ffull settlement to some #14.5 billion
OL,18,F` up from the #13.5 billion offered to
OL,19,FMr Healey but short of the #28 billion
OL,20,Fofficials previously said was needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FIn a major speech at a defence firm on
OL,8,FTuesday, Sir Keir will set out how the
OL,9,FDip will accelerate Britain's drone
OL,10,Fcapabilities, as wars in both Ukraine
OL,11,Fand Iran have seen widespread use of
OL,12,Fthe warfighting robots.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of the Dip's launch,
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister said: "This game-
OL,9,Fchanging investment will strengthen
OL,10,Four armed forces on land, at sea and
OL,11,Fin the air, ensuring our servicemen
OL,12,Fand women have the cutting-edge
OL,13,Fcapabilities they need to deter
OL,14,Fevolving threats and keep the British
OL,15,Fpeople safe.
OL,17,F"At the same time, we are backing
OL,18,FBritish innovation, British industry
OL,19,Fand British jobs and delivering
OL,20,Fopportunity to every corner of the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,F"Today's defence investment plan will
OL,8,Fhelp drive growth across the UK,
OL,9,Fgiving our industrial base the
OL,10,Fconfidence, certainty and support it
OL,11,Fneeds to develop and scale the
OL,12,Ftechnologies that will keep our
OL,13,Fcountry safe and secure long into the
OL,14,Ffuture."
OL,16,FMr Jarvis, the new defence secretary,
OL,17,Fhas spent his two weeks in the job
OL,18,F"refocusing" the Dip, Downing Street
OL,19,Fsaid, so that it will get the "latest
OL,20,Fkit" into the hands of the armed
OL,21,Fforces.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@HO]zD@AOUzD@LO]{D@_OU|D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,FThe Defence Secretary said: "Our armed
OL,8,Fforces are serving at an increasingly
OL,9,Fdangerous and unpredictable time. We
OL,10,Fare determined to give them what they
OL,11,Fneed as they serve with courage and
OL,12,Fexceptional skill to keep us safe.
OL,14,F"The character of warfare is rapidly
OL,15,Fchanging. In Ukraine and the Middle
OL,16,FEast, uncrewed systems are defining
OL,17,Fconflicts.
OL,26,@oD@]OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782857895
OL,3,CStarmer hails 'game-changing'
OL,4,Cinvestment as delayed defence plan to
OL,5,Cbe unveiled
OL,7,F"This largest ever UK investment into
OL,8,Fthese evolving technologies will help
OL,9,Four armed forces stay ahead of our
OL,10,Fadversaries, backed by the best of our
OL,11,Fdefence industry. We are giving our
OL,12,Fextraordinary people the equipment
OL,13,Fthey need to fight and win."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
